            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Code Review\",\n  \"approvals_required\": 2,\n  \"user_ids\": [12, 15]\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v4/projects/{{projectId}}/merge_requests/{{mergeRequestIid}}/approval_rules",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v4", "projects", "{{projectId}}", "merge_requests", "{{mergeRequestIid}}", "approval_rules"]
            },
            "description": "MR 개별 승인 규칙을 추가한다. name/approvals_required/user_ids/group_ids 설정. summary.md에 별도 응답 명세 없음 — 01번 List 응답 구조로 작성."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "201 Created",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "POST",
                "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Code Review\",\n  \"approvals_required\": 2,\n  \"user_ids\": [12]\n}" },
                "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v4/projects/{{projectId}}/merge_requests/{{mergeRequestIid}}/approval_rules", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v4", "projects", "{{projectId}}", "merge_requests", "{{mergeRequestIid}}", "approval_rules"] }
              },
              "status": "Created",
              "code": 201,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "body": "{\n  \"id\": 2,\n  \"name\": \"Code Review\",\n  \"rule_type\": \"regular\",\n  \"approvals_required\": 2\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "03. Retrieve a single MR approval rule",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v4/projects/{{projectId}}/merge_requests/{{mergeRequestIid}}/approval_rules/{{ruleId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v4", "projects", "{{projectId}}", "merge_requests", "{{mergeRequestIid}}", "approval_rules", "{{ruleId}}"]
            },
            "description": "단일 MR 승인 규칙 상세를 조회한다."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v4/projects/{{projectId}}/merge_requests/{{mergeRequestIid}}/approval_rules/{{ruleId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v4", "projects", "{{projectId}}", "merge_requests", "{{mergeRequestIid}}", "approval_rules", "{{ruleId}}"] }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "body": "{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"name\": \"Code Review\",\n  \"rule_type\": \"regular\",\n  \"approvals_required\": 2,\n  \"users\": [\n    { \"id\": 12, \"username\": \"kkh_ssafy\" }\n  ]\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "04. Update an MR approval rule",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"approvals_required\": 3,\n  \"user_ids\": [12, 15, 20]\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v4/projects/{{projectId}}/merge_requests/{{mergeRequestIid}}/approval_rules/{{ruleId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v4", "projects", "{{projectId}}", "merge_requests", "{{mergeRequestIid}}", "approval_rules", "{{ruleId}}"]
            },
            "description": "MR 승인 규칙을 수정한다. approvals_required(필수 승인 수) 등 변경. summary.md에 별도 명세 없음 — 02번 Create와 동일 필드 구조로 작성."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "PUT",
                "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
                "body": { "mode": "raw", "raw": "{\n  \"approvals_required\": 3\n}" },
                "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v4/projects/{{projectId}}/merge_requests/{{mergeRequestIid}}/approval_rules/{{ruleId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v4", "projects", "{{projectId}}", "merge_requests", "{{mergeRequestIid}}", "approval_rules", "{{ruleId}}"] }
              },
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "json",
              "body": "{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"name\": \"Code Review\",\n  \"approvals_required\": 3\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "05. Delete an MR approval rule",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v4/projects/{{projectId}}/merge_requests/{{mergeRequestIid}}/approval_rules/{{ruleId}}",
              "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"],
              "path": ["api", "v4", "projects", "{{projectId}}", "merge_requests", "{{mergeRequestIid}}", "approval_rules", "{{ruleId}}"]
            },
            "description": "MR 승인 규칙을 삭제한다."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "204 No Content",
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "DELETE",
                "header": [],
                "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v4/projects/{{projectId}}/merge_requests/{{mergeRequestIid}}/approval_rules/{{ruleId}}", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "v4", "projects", "{{projectId}}", "merge_requests", "{{mergeRequestIid}}", "approval_rules", "{{ruleId}}"] }
              },
              "status": "No Content",
              "code": 204,
              "_postman_previewlanguage": "text",
              "body": ""
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Project & Group Approval Settings (06 ~ 09)",
      "description": "프로젝트 및 그룹 기본 MR 승인 정책 조회/설정.",
      "item": [
